name: WOW Family Restaurant & Bar (Tiger Bar)

reviews.review_text: Nice place to sit and have good food and drinks.. price is reasonable.. ambience is very nice. Located by the roadside so easily visible. You can park your vehicle comfortably. Recommending the place for ones who go to visit Aguada Fort. while returning one can have lunch. Cocktails, mocktails and otherdrinks are served at the table. Fish cutlets are simply yumm..
Ambience is good. Food quality is ok-ok. Quantity is less. Fish thali not upto mark ,as per google review. Fish curry is like punjabi sabji gralvy.  Disappointed on this.

One of the best places for having goan fish curry, place is right on the main street and ample seating spaces available. Food is nice although service takes a little bit time, but all in all a good place to have a tummy full of food. Prices are reasonable. Do try the fish thalli.

description:
**WOW Family Restaurant & Bar (Tiger Bar): A Slice of Goan Hospitality**

Nestled conveniently near Aguada Fort in Goa, WOW Family Restaurant & Bar, affectionately known as Tiger Bar, boasts an inviting overall rating of 3.8 based on 1,066 reviews. Guests frequently highlight the restaurant’s relaxed atmosphere with tags like "music" (28 mentions), "Goan" (14), "thali" (9), and its prime location near the beautiful fort (8 mentions). This establishment presents itself not just as a dining option but as a memorable pit stop for those exploring the picturesque region.

### Ambiance & Design

WOW Family Restaurant & Bar greets its visitors with a cheerful ambiance, enhanced by a thoughtfully arranged roadside seating that is easily visible to passersby. The décor strikes a blend of casual comfort and vibrant Goan flair, setting the perfect backdrop for a laid-back meal. Photos shared by customers reflect a lively atmosphere, with charming arrangements of tables that suggest ample space for families and groups. The lighting seems warm and inviting, creating a welcoming vibe, and the background music subtly complements the culinary experience.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Tiger Bar heartily embraces Goan culinary traditions, particularly showcasing their fish dishes, which are often highlighted in reviews. Signature entries such as the fish thali and fish curry resonate with those in search of authentic Goan flavors. Diners have found the fish cutlets to be a standout, described as “simply yumm” by one enthusiastic patron. However, opinions vary, with some reviewers noting that the portion sizes could leave something to be desired, particularly for the fish thali, which has faced criticism for not meeting expectations. Yet, in the grand scheme, the value offered for the price is often praised as reasonable, making it a reliable stop for a satisfying Goan meal.

### Customer Experience & Service

Service at WOW Family Restaurant & Bar generally falls under the "good" category, albeit with occasional reports of delays. While enthusiastic staff members are often praised for their friendliness, a few guests have indicated that they experienced longer wait times for their meals. The restaurant appears to cater to both walk-in diners and those looking to reserve tables, making it adaptable to different dining preferences.

### Popularity & Reviews

Customer sentiment about WOW Family Restaurant & Bar is reflective of a mixed but mostly positive experience. The convenience of its location near tourist attractions like Aguada Fort and the reasonably priced menu have drawn many visitors. While some reviews express disappointment regarding specific dishes not meeting their expectations, many others commend the restaurant as a solid choice for travelers to satiate their cravings for authentic Goan cuisine. The presence of customer reviews on social media platforms amplifies its visibility and charm. Moreover, amazing food photography shared by patrons showcases the delightfully presented dishes and visually appealing surroundings.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Customer-provided images further enhance the vibrant narrative of WOW Family Restaurant & Bar. One photograph captures a beautifully arranged fish thali, brimming with colorful Goan delicacies that exemplify the culinary craftsmanship of the chef. An image of the restaurant's exterior offers insight into its accessibility and roadside charm. Furthermore, the interior shots depict a lively dining area filled with guests enjoying their meals, encapsulating the essence of a warm family restaurant atmosphere.

In conclusion, WOW Family Restaurant & Bar holds its ground as a delightful dining option in Goa. With its appealing fusion of Goan cuisine, vibrant ambiance, and commendable service, it promises a memorable experience for both locals and tourists alike. Whether you're unwinding after a day of sightseeing or indulging in the flavors of Goa, Tiger Bar proves to be a worthwhile visit.
